  "wechat_html": "<img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzXgUR7FJnf11qGIo8nmKt6RxibXrb5s4RFb9UZ9UOHQy7fqQyI377Licw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'><section style='padding:0;'><section style=\"margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f6efe4 0%,#fbf8f2 58%,#ffffff 100%);padding:1px;color:#1f2937;\"><section style=\"width:100%;margin:0;\"><section style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.16);box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:relative;background:#d6d3d1;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-13/hf-event-00.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block;\"></div><section style=\"padding:16px 12px 10px;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:#111827;color:#f9fafb;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">History Today</div><h1 style=\"font-size:29px;line-height:1.22;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#111827;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;\">历史上的今天：哈佛学院正式得名</h1><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#475569;margin:0;\">1639年的今天，哈佛学院正式以约翰·哈佛的名字命名。</p></section><section style=\"padding:0 10px 12px;\"><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">在学术界的历史上，许多伟大的学府都有着深厚的渊源。1639年的3月13日，对于这所世界闻名的学府来说是一个重要的里程碑，它在这一天正式获得了自己的名字。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-13/hf-event-01.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">这所学院为了纪念一位慷慨的捐赠者——牧师约翰·哈佛，决定将学院正式命名为哈佛学院。这一举动不仅是对其贡献的认可，也为后来的学术殿堂奠定了深厚的基础。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-13/hf-event-02.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">除了学术史上的这一重要时刻，历史上这一天还发生过其他值得关注的事件。例如在1567年的3月13日，奥斯特韦尔战役爆发，这场冲突在历史上被认为是八十年战争的开端。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-13/hf-event-03.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">此外，历史上在这一天也诞生了一些重要人物。例如在1615年的3月13日，后来成为罗马主教的教宗英诺森十二世出生，他在17世纪的宗教历史上留下了自己的印记。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-13/hf-event-04.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">历史长河中的每一天都承载着不同的记忆，从学术殿堂的命名到战争的爆发，这些事件共同构成了人类历史的多元面貌。回顾这些往事，让我们对过去有了更深刻的理解。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-13/hf-event-05.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div></section></section></section></section></section><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzk57DCmhVC16o9ILH0Tn1YPEiarfLRRQSVFN2mJdeYibGnBPialPIzvojw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'>"
